songs.title: Crazed Madman Intro
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: DJ Green Lantern]
The views and opinions expressed on this mixtape are those of a crazed madman, who just doesn't give a fuck. He goes by the name of

Royce the five-nine, Nickel Nine
This is now The Bar Exam two
Get ya', get ya' pencils ready
Sixty minutes on the timer, let's get it
